{
    "title": "אֵלֶֽיךָ אֶקְרָא יָהּ | Elekha Eqra Yah, a piyyut by Rabbi Shlomoh Zrihen (20th c.)",
    "author": "Adam Zagoria-Moffet (translation)",
    "coauthors": [
