            "bio": "Rabbi Shlomoh Zrihen (שלמה זריהן; b?,1939 - d.2017), was a son of Rabbi Mosheh Zrihen, chief rabbi of Marrakesh, Morocco, and the composer of the well-loved piyyut, \"Elekha Ekra Yah El Nora.\"",
